{"id":660200,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/12/【cdtv】尖椒部落-富士康工厂的女厕文学/","date":"2020-12-05T20:26:41Z","modified":"2020-12-05T20:26:41Z","title":"【CDTV】尖椒部落 | 富士康工厂的“女厕文学”","content":"<p>摘要：有欣赏价值才称之为厕所文学。</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class='youtube-player' width='1080' height='608' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/5kVrbIytbgI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=zh-CN&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent' allowfullscreen='true' style='border:0;' sandbox='allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation'></iframe></span></p>\n<p><video src=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Mt4y1v73p\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\"></video></p>\n<p>日常生活中，我们总能看到各种各样形形色色的小广告，而在公共卫生间，更不用说了，通常以涂鸦式文字，打油诗，黄色/骗人广告的形式出现&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_660201\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-660201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/12/Screen-Shot-2020-12-05-at-7.58.14-PM-e1607198337631.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"size-full wp-image-660201\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-660201\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">赤裸裸将女性进行明码标价的</p></div><br />\n<div id=\"attachment_660202\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-660202\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/12/Screen-Shot-2020-12-05-at-7.59.33-PM-e1607198464565.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"size-full wp-image-660202\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-660202\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">暗含性意味的骚扰</p></div><br />\n<div id=\"attachment_660203\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-660203\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/12/Screen-Shot-2020-12-05-at-8.01.46-PM-e1607198594766.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"size-full wp-image-660203\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-660203\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">还有把女性进行标签贩卖的骗局</p></div></p>\n<p>如此看来，厕所里的文字创作大多都是低俗不堪的，但如果出现在特定地点特定场所，会不会有所不一样？</p>\n<p>正所谓有欣赏价值才能称之为厕所文学。小椒最近发现了一位宝藏up主：独行侠二十一。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_660204\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-660204\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/12/Screen-Shot-2020-12-05-at-8.03.50-PM-e1607198679697.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"386\" class=\"size-full wp-image-660204\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-660204\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">这位up主是一位来自富士康的女工友</p></div>\n<p>这位up主是一位来自富士康的女工友，一直用视频的形式详细记录下了自己在工厂的真实工作生活，而最新的一期视频正是从工厂女厕里挑选了一些涂鸦文字做成了一期非常有意义的视频。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_660205\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-660205\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/12/FireShot-Capture-111-富士康工厂的女厕文学-mp.weixin.qq_.com_-e1607198936877.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1095\" class=\"size-full wp-image-660205\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-660205\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">或许你也有常看的视频博主吗？欢迎大家留言评论安利给小椒，本椒立马前去关注一波！点赞三连！</p></div>\n","author":1061,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,38927],"tags":[24371,22164,32560,10628,32767,11527]}